{"tid":1606901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"社運素人有感-聽日不如玩空城計？","createTime":"2019-09-30T16:28:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T21:20:38.000Z","uid":314545,"like":5,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"b89dd0526932a69e323013ad2892bba8da043525","tid":1606901,"uid":314545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:28:59.000Z","msg":"社運素人有感。既然而家吹到咁行，聽日有大事發生，黨鐵、商場都要關閉避風頭，不如聽日就一個都唔好出，等佢地白忙一場。敵進我退，存己精銳。<br />\n<br />\n老老實實，由612到而家都四個月，成件事模式化咗，就係weekend出嚟，之後俾啲港共爪牙（popo)追打、打到頭破血流，虐待被自殺，好慘烈，然後大家又好嬲，要出嚟，無限輪迴。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n既然現階段武力勝不過啲爪牙，而家美國又即張過加辣版人權法，嚴懲中共港共，而家應該整理啲pk popo罪證，做好文宣工作，全球廣傳，等佢地世界之大，都無其容身之所。與此同時，思考下一步行動，好過week week送頭，賠了夫人又折兵，而港共爪牙依然故我咁仆街。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嬲，好嬲，好鬼嬲，係嬲呀，但嬲完都要冷靜，諗下下一步點做，個個weekend俾啲仆街仆頭同虐待都唔係路，班仆街真係唔當示威者係人。香港人咁醒目，無理由嘢嘢送死。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"200593167c56ea994ec472d03a8c9fc9192f6777","tid":1606901,"uid":33875,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:33:18.000Z","msg":"黨慶邊可能唔搞大佢，空城就無可能，即時轉個生場都可以"},{"pid":"a4c073d4307b4d02d0bad75bf984efb6d9036e12","tid":1606901,"uid":8170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:34:47.000Z","msg":"狼來了加空城計都幾好玩，最後成街關晒門關晒站，啲狗企晒喺度唔知做乜。"},{"pid":"3071ac9929a0694060610984644dc36e910a0e5b","tid":1606901,"uid":69159,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:37:16.000Z","msg":"你都係做返素人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b4c891458d4ce1debecc4c883c79bcb1812d117","tid":1606901,"uid":296246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:44:47.000Z","msg":"講好左要賀佢老母咯"},{"pid":"15140f9137e6b096edbdeebc3308dee0ae18256e","tid":1606901,"uid":75127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:46:05.000Z","msg":"其他日子可能 但國慶就一定要落佢面"},{"pid":"db3d2e681fdb128721492c0fe009ffcb2c98e490","tid":1606901,"uid":261478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:46:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c28ca040e78d6daa4bd1f7a8890f39fafc2e975f","tid":1606901,"uid":242734,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:47:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拉，on9 post ,日後fake 埋自己人"},{"pid":"522790f401986591d91fde6324308117de0f4008","tid":1606901,"uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:47:51.000Z","msg":"又開新 acc 帶風向"},{"pid":"afa2e066156d589ea9902ef49ad672eb7935390b","tid":1606901,"uid":60749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:47:55.000Z","msg":"咪撚鳩 吹咗咁耐 邊有得返轉頭<br />\n全城狂賀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n善用不推文回復拉低個post"},{"pid":"026325c9c0a395fc9e154323b5f6877730c9d2ae","tid":1606901,"uid":116511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:48:18.000Z","msg":"拉<br />\nOn撚9"},{"pid":"4ab202d033a7a1c6f4ad3352eba7a4d629916d87","tid":1606901,"uid":257972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:49:26.000Z","msg":"賀佢老母啊 空乜撚野城計"},{"pid":"8b3d82a2448934eb0c9a70ce8657121f0b4f4266","tid":1606901,"uid":295124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:56:11.000Z","msg":"想智取前唔該認真考慮下"},{"pid":"e7c7e75f032e7679213af33bb0e3dda01dfc2708","tid":1606901,"uid":6352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:06:36.000Z","msg":"唔好on9，空你老母！"},{"pid":"eb41dad7cdcc5ec4f3ab50d5629a5c1a84d0eb0e","tid":1606901,"uid":134744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:08:59.000Z","msg":"如果聽日唔係十月一都可以諗下<br />\n但聽日一定要賀佢老母"},{"pid":"0c31a1c7b12630b75906f703f157350c8ec7aa8b","tid":1606901,"uid":72502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:10:36.000Z","msg":"收皮啦"},{"pid":"15b895f448212fb8ad2d99d3da8cff7df1c93372","tid":1606901,"uid":20696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:12:25.000Z","msg":"近幾個月最有意義嘅大日子就係十一<br />\n十一都唔搞大佢<br />\n之後仲有咩日子有得發大嚟搞？<br />\n如果聽日唔係十一都仲有得諗下⋯⋯<br />\n同埋有啲野真係 一鼓作氣，再而衰，三而竭。話就話空城，但心知肚明係見重兵放棄，棄得一次就有兩次，慢慢就冇人再出嚟，因為覺得大家都唔firm<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw不推文"},{"pid":"45f1b5da41d83a1273c7551c9bb4b4d8c726ab70","tid":1606901,"uid":27485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:12:29.000Z","msg":"素你老母 有邊個唔係素人"},{"pid":"b69f73215193d6503f0e1ff4ea10bcb774aadc8e","tid":1606901,"uid":249026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:13:55.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"2bf2017d9ec7ffbf3992492bd5d454a70efccc35","tid":1606901,"uid":321837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:16:08.000Z","msg":"邊有可能,聽日沙田日馬繼續跑.跑少一日少幾億.<br />\n好快干塘糧都無得出,草都無得食."},{"pid":"f1f3fe67ec8a2cd98bbfef83c68827d48dc7fa28","tid":1606901,"uid":39796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:16:18.000Z","msg":"用下腦啦on9仔"},{"pid":"3b97badadcf33fdc5cfb8739ee99f19a850bcb85","tid":1606901,"uid":271088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3071ac9929a0694060610984644dc36e910a0e5b","tid":1606901,"uid":69159,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:37:16.000Z","msg":"你都係做返素人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:18:14.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"b653d9d72e3fc6575bdf2aa962251cbd5035d9b0","tid":1606901,"uid":314545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T21:20:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n落面嘅嘢，大燃把嘢可以做，跟岳字少年話齋，珍惜生命呀老友，唔好講到聽日係end game咁。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/273813022746352/posts/2356156891178611?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F273813022746352%2Fposts%2F2356156891178611%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6pKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=ac25466b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/273813022746352/posts/2356156891178611?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n由612到而家，流水社運，無名無姓無大台，唔會擔心無人出嚟，而家擔心嘅係無謂犧牲。有勇都要有謀，一味死衝，咁同野豬受驚係咁衝有咩分別，野豬最後都係俾人射低呀。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1606981/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1606981/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n//如果個問題癥結係唔夠震撼力嘅話，我地聽日根本有好好嘅主題俾我地發揮，就係國殤日，點解唔發大呢個主題嚟搞？全港灑溪錢，踩國旗踩維尼，路祭CCP同刁敗敗，掟到成地都係白色水彈。有POPO嚟就散水，甚至留係屋企灑到周街溪錢，播喪樂，搞到全香港成個中共殯儀館咁，根本唔駛一百萬人係港島曬馬都已經夠曬震撼。<br />\n<br />\n聽日係中共嘅國殤日，唔係我地嘅國殤日呀！邊個準你地End game？你死咗邊個同中共玩落去？傻架？記住我地運動嘅宗旨係Be Water，唔係同中共，更唔係同班警狗硬碰硬。知唔知道呀你班傻豬！！！//"}]}